
# Sohail Ansari - Portfolio

Welcome to my professional portfolio website built with HTML, CSS, and a touch of JavaScript. This site highlights my background, skills, and contact information, and includes a downloadable resume.

## Features

- Responsive design for all devices  
- Toggle between light and dark mode (moon/sun icon)  
- Downloadable resume (PDF)  
- Clean, modern UI with lavender theme

## How to View

Visit the live site at:  
https://sohailansari56.github.io/Sohail-Ansari-Portfolio/
